Your Penis Name is: Beefy McManstick

Get your own Penis Name

LOL! Also my life's theme song, the song that was #1 on my 18th birthday was in the US "It Wasn't Me" by Shaggy, and in the UK "Rollin" by Limp Bizkit.

Well, last night I met Stacey's friend Serah, and I think things went well. She was very pretty, she laughed at my jokes, and I think she might actually like football. She ended up telling me that her first impression of me was that I was really hot, really funny and it was awesome that I was such a huge LSU football fan, she said overall I was an A+. Rock on! We went eat at Chevy's and then chilled at Morning Call for a little while, we were gonna go out afterwards but her dad wouldn't let her go so I ended up going home which was probably a good thing cause I was super tired, slept for like ten and a half hours, it was so nice to sleep that well. Ria had wanted me to go out with her uptown, but I had to turn her down cause I already had prior plans, and had I not been tired, afterwards I would've either met her wherever she was or would have met some of my friends in the quarter, but like I said super tired, so sorry guys. Also at one point last night Ria kept calling me up and text messaging me to find out who I thought was cuter between her and Serah, and I think I upset her cause I didn't answer her question. I kept telling her that both she and Serah were pretty, which is true; I was the cuter one, which is true; and that I'm not going to sit there and compare people, which is also true. I don't like to do that, I don't care if I'm comparing Heidi Klum to Rosie O'Donnel, if I have to tell either one of them or either one of them would find out my answer I would never say what I thought, simple as that. So many women, so little me, LOL, j/k. As a matter of fact this seems to happen often but before you think here goes again, I really don't like this situation cause too many people can get hurt. Besides I usually end up with no one in the end so let me have my fun while I can. Oh well, until next time, probably won't do anything tonight, my life is just boring like that.

Well apparently within the last few days I have become a man whore. Just cause I have the ability to attract girls doesn't make me a whore. I'm not saying it's a bad thing I'm just not a whore. School has been boring as usual, today I stayed super late and was the entertainment for a group of people, it was awesome, then I went to the mall and bought a new pair of shoes cause my shoes I was wearing at the moment started to fall apart. Last night I went shoot pool and whooped some ass, then I went to Tucks to meet Ria, she was there cause it was ladies night and the second I got there I helped Ria and her friend Rachel win a game of pool in which some guys were manhandling them, in one turn, a thank you. Then I had fun dancing the night away and I tried that new Budweiser select, it was pretty good. I had to carry Ria to her friends car and then I went home. Tonight I went shoot pool again and whooped ass once again, the funniest part of the night was either the time I beat this guy Dennis without making a single shot or the time I finished off the last 3 balls on the table, each one an incredibly hard shot, to beat Patrick and then I looked up and he was just staring at the table with his jaw basically on the ground and all he could say was, "That's it I'm done." Larry and I talked him into another couple of games, all of which I won. Wow, I am the man, scratch that, the jury shall ignore that last comment on the basis of self inconcededness. Although thats not really a word, I think it works in that situation, so leave me alone Webster.

I want to apologize for the last post, it was something that I thought had to be done, and one day after it seems that everyone is okay after it. I'm very happy that my friends reacted the way they did, I hope this lasts. 
Well, I woke up late for school today, really late. Missed my first two classes and then my meeting, then left early to go home and cut the grass and pick up my check from work. Very boring and uneventful day, didn't even get a chance to see anyone that was really affected by the previous post, so all my assuming that everything is fine now is based off of internet chats with a few people. For now all I have to worry about is waking up on time tomorrow. Hopefully this weekend will be fun. I know Pat won't get drunk or go to a strip club for his 21st birthday celebration, but hopefully we can get a bunch of friends together and just do something fun this weekend with him for his birthday. 
I've come to the realization that I suck at shooter games, but no worries cause I would challenge anyone to a Madden or NCAA college football game and I would probably own you. Put it this way, Pat isn't that bad at Madden but when he played me one time he had the Panthers (2nd best rated team on the game) and I had the Berlin Thunder (A sub par NFL Europe team), we're talking a 99 rating compared to a 56 rating. He quit at half time cause I had a 21-0 lead on him.

Well I had school as usual, and as usual there was more drama than I want to deal with going on among my friends. I can't stand it when all this shit is going down. I am really sick of it and if it doesn't get better soon i'm just gonna start hanging out somewhere else at school. I love my friends but sometimes they can really let things get to them too much and they don't let things go. First, I don't know why John has such resentment for Monica, he broke up with her and she is over it, just try to act a little more mature and treat her at least like a human being, I mean you claimed to have loved her not too long ago. Second, Kristin needs to realize that Monica only told me about her "bad experience with the law" because she assumed that I already knew cause she read it on her journal, that's why when Monica was talking to me she asked me if Kristin was ok, she assumed I had already talked to Kristin, and I was like what do you mean what happened to Kristin, and she told me so that I wouldnt be worried. Sure, Monica could have told me to call Kristin and find out but she didn't and she told me this over the phone so no one else found out until Kristin made mention of it at school on wednesday. I try to do all I can at the table to make people laugh, and with all this bullshit happening its been really hard to find reasons why to make these people happy, when it seems as if they are just hell bent on being pissed off. I had always said that Patrick would blow some things out of proportion, little did I realize he was one of the ones who let things aggravate him the least, I mean he still talks to me and I've done worse things to him than anyone else at the table has done to any other person. So people need to learn to chill the fuck out, there is nothing in life that happens to you on such a small level that should get you pissed off for this long. Life is short, learn to enjoy it and learn to let others enjoy it. If you don't like someone learn to deal with it and at least treat them like a human, everyone in the world no matter who they are deserves that.

Oh yeah, other things at school happened, Ria was asking me if I liked Lauren, the one with a boyfriend, and yet I still sensed that she likes me. It's so hard being sexy, it really is. But seriously I am kinda excited about this weekend, but I am also kinda scared. It always happens this way, either the girl likes me more than I like her or vice versa, and I can't really say which situation is harder. But I'm not gonna worry about it much, just gonna enjoy it. I also get to meet Katie's sister Sony, and Patrick's birthday is thursday, he'll be 21, and I won't feel so old anymore. Oh well, until next time, and hopefully I won't be bitching as much next time, but I just had to get all that off my chest. I apologize, but I really do love all my friends, every last one of them, even Dominick, but especially John ;P.

Wow, you would think that this would have been a great day due to the fact that 3 of my 4 classes were canceled today, but it wasn't. It was kind of a boring day, but I think things that happened the night before affected it. I apparently have a special gift to be able to annoy any girl that likes me. Apparently I made a promise, when I really didn't, that I didn't keep and that really pissed off this girl that I had a date set up with for today, but she ended up canceling because of the "broken promise". No worries though, one of my friends is gonna try to set me up with her friend, and I'm kinda excited about that. Also, there are these two girls at school that I met just recently that kinda seem to like me. I don't know if only one likes me and which one at that or if both like me, but one has a boyfriend but I am still unsure. Work today was pretty slow and I'm not sure what I am gonna do tonight, if anything. If I end up doing something you will hear about it in a later posting. Until then pray that you have better luck with the opposite sex than I do, cause for right now it seems like I am one of those royal guards in England, I stand there and look pretty, but I don't get much action, and I may be missing some action cause I can't move.

I am no longer a journal virgin. Now brace yourselves you are about to enter unchartered territory, my brain. It is something so complex that even i get lost in myself sometimes. 
Well, today was kind of a boring day so far, went to school and it rained. At school I took a test and almost fell asleep in another class. In the Cove, AKA my friends and I's hangout at school, I did my usual chillen and simply enjoying time with friends. Although today was kinda slow at the table cause just about everyone was playing magic and I don't really play that. My friend John must have been in kind of a bad mood today cause I made one comment about him that was supposed to be a compliment and he took it as an insult and started bitchin me out. So I got up and put him in his place. Actually I just told him I was giving him a compliment and he was like oh. So shigity shigity shigity shwaaa John. LOL. Probably gonna go to my friend Paul's house tonight to play some games of the board variety. In my next entry I will probably tell you how my date that I have planned for tomorrow went and how much shit I may end up putting myself in if I like the girl that my friend will be attempting to set me up with next week. Until then enjoy life and the women it provides you.
